                                        <span class="title_help">Guidelines for Participating in Tours</span>


                                    <!---19-->
                                                        
                                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading19">
                                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                                        <a class="collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse19" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse19">
                                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/images/icons/bullet.png")" class="small-icon">
                                            What should I keep in mind while participating in tour?

                                        </a>
                                        </h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapse19" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading19">
                                        <div class="new_panel_body">
                                                      
                                        The 5 most important things to remember are:

                                        <ol type='a'>

                                            <li><span class="boldIt"> Be on time: </span> plan ahead to ensure that you will reach the meet up location on time. Be sure to have the guide send you detailed directions and a map to your email before the day of the tour. If you are having trouble finding the place or will be late for whatever reason, please communicate with the guide directly or with Kootour so we may contact the guide.
                                            </li>

                                            <li><span class="boldIt"> Communicate your goals: </span> let the guide know what sort of tour you’d like. Do you prefer a lot of information or just the basics? Any areas of interest you want highlighted during the tour?

                                            </li>

                                            <li><span class="boldIt"> Pay attention to the guide’s information: </span> while some tours and activities may have less risks, it is still important to follow the safety and cultural tips given to you by the guide.


                                            </li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>
                                    </div>


                                    <!---20-->
