                                    <div id="collapse20" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading20">
                                        <div class="new_panel_body">
                                        First attempt to contact the guide yourself by emailing or calling him/her. If you are unable to do either, try using a public phone, a calling card or simply asking a nearby storekeeper. If you are still unable to contact the guide, send us an email to <a href="mailto:contact@kootour.com">contact@kootour.com</a> or call +1(604)683-6450. If we are unable to contact the guide or find someone who can replace them on that tour, we will proceed to issue a full refund or help you book a different tour if you prefer.
                                    </div>
                                    </div>


